Package net.fortuna.ical4j.model

Class PropertyBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fortuna.ical4j.model.AbstractContentBuilder
      • net.fortuna.ical4j.model.PropertyBuilder
  • public class PropertyBuilder
extends AbstractContentBuilder
    Provides a configurable builder for creating Property instances from String values. You can specify an arbitrary list of supported property factories, and a list of property names to ignore.
